author: Ishika Jain
title: 7 Must-Know Important Tips For A Memorable First Time Journey To Kurseong Of West Bengal
description: In the eastern folds of the Himalayas lies a captivating hill station - Kurseong. The serene atmosphere perfectly paired with eye-catching landscapes make it an unmissable spot. Blanketed with opulent tea gardens, this soothing retreat of West Bengal promises weather that pleases the soul. Offering stunning vistas that can leave any first-time visitor in awe, Kurseong sure is a shining jewel tucked away in the state's crown. Pack your bags and get set for an unforgettable journey exploring this picture-perfect town.
label: POSITIVE
